rating 
Behavior: global 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Check unit rating. Rating is increased for killing enemies, decreased 
 for killing friendlies (see Rating Values). Can be changed via addRating 
 by the mission designer.  
The rating of the player is displayed as the "score" at the end of the mission 
. Via Description.ext one can define how many points it takes to get a perfect 
 score, as well as the number of stars. 
Syntax:  
 Number = rating unitName 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object 
Return Value: 
 Number